<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.6">
<l>keṇṭaiyuṅ kuṟaḷum puḷḷuṅ kēḻalu mariyum māvum</l>
<l>aṇṭamuñ cuṭaru mallā vāṟṟalu māya ventai</l>
<l>ōṇṭiṟal teṉṉa ṉōṭa vaṭavara cōṭṭaṅ kaṇṭa</l>
<l>tiṇṭiṟa lāḷar nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat taṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, besides a fish, a dwarf, a bird, boar, lion, and horse,</l>
<l>The sky, and the sun, became [all] that is possible,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr with those of powerful strength</l>
<l>Who saw the routing of the northern king,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the brilliant, strong southern lord [also] ran.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
